Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.54,0:22:15.50,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}I wanna talk with you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.71,0:22:19.50,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}待ち合わせは何時？（10時）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.75,0:22:21.67,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}駅前に集合（OK！）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.80,0:22:25.26,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}着いたら教えて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.38,0:22:27.18,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}使い慣れたスタンプで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.43,0:22:29.80,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}話合えちゃうスタンスが本当
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.01,0:22:33.56,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}心地良くて愛しい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.06,0:22:37.60,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}一人胸にしまいこんだ言葉も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.23,0:22:41.86,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}上手くいかない減らない悩み事も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.23,0:22:48.28,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}全部忘れて遊びに行きたいね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.70,0:22:54.79,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}心のメモリア
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.79,0:22:57.87,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}笑顔が溢れるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.16,0:23:02.09,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}冗談混じりで頷く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.29,0:23:06.01,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}何気ないありふれたやり取りが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.17,0:23:11.22,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}心のメモリア
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.22,0:23:14.31,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}涙が零れても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.60,0:23:16.81,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}頑張れるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.81,0:23:20.52,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}君がくれた今日が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.77,0:23:23.36,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}優しくてありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.36,0:23:24.82,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Let's hang out
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.40,0:23:29.24,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}I wanna talk with you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.71,0:22:19.50,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}约好的时间是几点（十点）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.75,0:22:21.67,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}在车站前集合（OK）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.80,0:22:25.26,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}到了就告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.38,0:22:27.18,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}能够拿用惯了的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.43,0:22:29.80,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}来交谈心事的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.01,0:22:33.56,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}实在让人舒心爱怜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.06,0:22:37.60,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}独自藏在自己心里的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.23,0:22:41.86,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}过得不顺 越来越多的烦心事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.23,0:22:48.28,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}想要全都忘掉 和你一起出去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.70,0:22:54.79,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}留在心中的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.79,0:22:57.87,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}是洋溢在脸上的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.16,0:23:02.09,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}是半开玩笑的点头
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.29,0:23:06.01,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}是不经意间毫不稀奇的交谈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.17,0:23:11.22,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}留在心中的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.22,0:23:14.31,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}哪怕泪水夺眶而出
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.60,0:23:16.81,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}也能够努力下去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.81,0:23:20.52,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}你留给我的今天是如此温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.77,0:23:23.36,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}谢谢你
